information: Headland Trading was founded with a vision to meet the growing demand of healthy fruits and vegetables in Spain and the EU. In order to promote and support the finest grown local produce, most of our suppliers are family-run farms in the MENA region. We strive to inspire modernisation, and through globalisation, introduce new and exotic fresh produce from various origins to the EU market. We specialize in strategic sourcing, import, and delivery of fresh, dried, and frozen fruits and vegetables from the Middle East and North Africa region (MENA). Using our thorough sourcing process, we find the best cultivators and producers of the freshest, tastiest, and healthiest fruits and vegetables. Our main Products: Dates, Sweet Potatoes, Pomegranate, Iceberg lettuce, Eggplant, Green Beans, Red & Gold Onions, Red & white cabbage, Garlic, Citrus, Watermelons, Melons, and Mangoes.
